OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a dry and bright day
OL,6,Fwith sunny spells. Cloud will build
OL,7,Fthrough the afternoon, with sunny
OL,8,Fspells becoming more limited. Moderate
OL,9,Fto fresh southerly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FIt will be a largely dry and
OL,12,Fcloudy night with some clear intervals
OL,13,Fpossible. A few spots of light rain
OL,14,Fare also possible. Moderate southerly
OL,15,Fwinds.
OL,16,
OL,17,CMonday:FA mostly cloudy day with some
OL,18,Fbright or sunny intervals breaking
OL,19,Fthrough. Largely dry but a few
OL,20,Foutbreaks of rain possible through the
OL,21,Fday. Moderate to fresh southerly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
